# DEVELOPER DOCUMENTATION (Technical Guide)

## 📌 Project Overview
This project digitizes the **José Rizal Guided Walk** into an interactive virtual tour using multimedia, 3D assets, and web-based tools.

### Technologies Used
*   **Thinglink:** Interactive platform for the virtual experience.
*   **GitHub:** Version control for documentation and asset tracking.
*   **360° Camera:** Used for high-quality environmental image capture.
*   **3D Renders:** Integration of PNG and MP4 assets.

